        jLabel5.setText("<html>The weight loss phases are primarily based on eating unlimited high-protein foods and mandatory oat bran.\nThe other phases involve adding non-starchy vegetables followed by some carbs and fat. Later on, there will be fewer and fewer pure protein days to maintain your new weight.</html>");
